ReferenceDataLoadLog.name: ReferenceDataLoadLog
ReferenceDataLoadLog.description: Represents information about the history of loading reference data for emissions factors.

DatasetExternalIdentifier.description: The unique external identifier for the dataset.

DatasetType.description: Specifies the type of the dataset.

Description.description: The description of the dataset load.

ErrorMessage.description: The error messages generated while loading dataset, if any.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp for when the current user last viewed a record related to this record.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp for when the current user last viewed this record. If this value is null, this record might only have been referenced (LastReferencedDate) and not viewed.

LoadDateTime.description: The date and time when the dataset was loaded.

LoadStatus.description: Specifies the status of loading the dataset.

LoadedById.description: The user who loaded the dataset.

Name.description: The name of the dataset log record.

OwnerId.description: The ID of the user who owns this record.

Provider.description: The organization that's providing this dataset.

TotalLoadedRecordCount.description: The total number of records that were updated or inserted.

TotalSkippedRecordCount.description: The total number of records that were skipped.

TotalTime.description: The time duration taken to load the dataset.

UsageType.description: The usage of the dataset load log.

VersionNameTag.description: The name tag of the dataset version.

VersionNumber.description: The version number for the dataset.
